    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.10) / (tmp + 0.05 * v2 + 0.67)) / tmp)
    tmp = ((0.60 / (tmp + 0.44 + v2 + 0.75)) * wp.exp((v2 + 0.64 / v0 + 0.53)))
    v1 = (v1 - wp.exp(0.99))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = (0.38 * wp.cos(0.45))
    v1 = 0.89
    v0 = ((0.13 + (tmp + 0.19 / v2 + 0.81)) - wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.85)))
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
